text: Retimohnia acadiana is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Garcia E.F. (2008). Four new buccinid species (Gastropoda: Buccinidae) from the western Atlantic. Novapex 9(4): 141-148 ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Retimohnia acadiana
